Piers forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Obstagoon}}, {{form|Toxtricity|Low Key Form}} {{p|Toxtricity}}, and {{p|Skuntank}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Piers became a playable sync pair on February 18, 2021.

Piers has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]] and the [[villain arc]].

